---
title: Sweet Potato Niçoise Salad with Lemon-Dijon Dressing
description: We took some liberties with the classic French salad Niçoise, but worry not, this salad is worthy in its own right. Roasted sweet potato marries with traditional components like tomatoes and green beans for an unexpectedly harmonious medley. The entire salad is amped up by a creamy lemon- Dijon dressing. Bon appétit!
